                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing phosgene through CO2 electrolysis two-step method",
                    "一种CO2电解两步法制光气的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a method for preparing phosgene by a CO2 electrolysis two-step method. According to the method, an electrolysis reactor is divided into upper and lower parts; the lower part is an electrolytic tank chamber, CO2 is electrolyzed to prepare CO, and chlorate is electrolyzed to prepare Cl2; the upper part is a phosgenation reaction chamber, and under the catalytic action of an electric field, CO generated by electrolysis and Cl2 are subjected to a catalytic reaction to prepare phosgene; the upper and lower parts of the reactor are separated by a hydrophobic breathable diaphragm; an electrolytic cell chamber in the reactor is divided into a chamber A and a chamber B. The chamber A is a gas feeding chamber and is connected with a gas diffusion cathode. And the chamber B is an electrolysis chamber and is a cathode and anode coexistence chamber, and no diaphragm is arranged between the cathode and the anode. According to the technology, CO2 electrolysis and phosgene preparation are achieved in the same electric field and the same device, the Faraday efficiency of cathode hydrogen evolution is smaller than 0.0001%, the corrosion risk of an electrolytic bath is low, the technology is simple, and carbon neutralization can be assisted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种CO2电解两步法制光气的方法。该方法将电解反应器分为上下两部分；下部为电解槽腔室，进行CO2电解制CO、氯化盐电解制Cl2；上部为光气化反应腔室，在电场催化作用下，将电解产生的CO与Cl2催化反应制光气；反应器上下两部分通过疏水透气隔膜分隔开；反应器中电解槽腔室分为A、B两个腔室，A腔室为气体进料腔室，连接气体扩散阴极；B腔室为电解腔室，为阴极和阳极共存腔室，阴极阳极之间无隔膜。该工艺在同一个电场同一个设备内实现CO2电解和光气制备，阴极析氢法拉第效率小于0.0001%，电解槽腐蚀风险低，工艺简单且可助力碳中和。"
                }
            ]
